acl.description: The S3 predefined collection of grantees and permissions set for the bucket, also referred to as a [Canned ACL](https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AmazonS3/latest/userguide/acl-overview.html#canned-acl).

cors_enabled.description: If `true`, cross-origin resource sharing (CORS) is enabled for all origins in the bucket.
